info.name: Aloo 65
info.description: Crispy fried chunks of potato, stir fried with freshly chopped chillies and curry leaves, seasoned with a traditional mix of spices.

info.name: Chilli Paneer
info.description: Chilli Paneer is a popular Indo-Chinese dish where cubes of fried crispy paneer are tossed in a spicy sauce made with soy sauce, vinegar, chili sauce

info.name: Paneer 65
info.description: Crispy fried cottage cheese chunks stir fried with freshly chopped chillies and curry leaves, seasoned with a traditiona mix of spices.

info.name: Chilli Chicken
info.description: A south-east Asian staple of crispy batter friend chicken chunks tossed in a spicy mix of garlic, chilli, onion and peppers.

info.name: Chicken 65
info.description: Delicious and succulent chunks of chicken marinated in yoghurt and stir fried in a traditional mix of spices, chillies and the hero ingredient which binds it all together - curry leaves.

info.name: Chicken Dry Roast
info.description: Diced cubes of chicken cooked with a traditional, spicy and fresh mix of spices and herbs - fried in sumptuous quantities of fresh ghee till crisp. Topped with curry leaves, green chilies and cashew nuts.

info.name: Andhra Chicken Fry
info.description: A peppery fried preparation with diced cubes of chicken, flavoursome blended spices, and fresh whole spices - fried till well cooked with a delicious brown skin.

info.name: Chicken Lolipop (6 Pcs)
info.description: Juicy batter friend chicken winglets cooked to perfection in a traditional mix of spices, all ready to be picked up and devoured.

info.name: Andhra Mutton Fry
info.description: A peppery fried preparation with tender diced cubes of mutton, flavoursome blended spices, and fresh whole spices - fried till well cooked.

info.name: Chicken Seekh Kebab
info.description: Skewered minced chicken roll cooked into perfection in a tandoor.

info.name: Mutton Seekh Kebab
info.description: Zestful, fresh green chilli and secret spice infused,mutton mince kabab of the finest quality.

info.name: Paneer Butter Masala
info.description: Fresh cottage cheese cooked in tomato puree and cream finished with butter in indian thick masala.

info.name: Egg Curry
info.description: A traditional curry with delicate boiled eggs with crispy skin immersed in a spicy onion and tomato gravy seasoned with chilies, ginger and garlic.

info.name: Chicken Chettinadu
info.description: Simple and spicy chicken curry prepared as per South India? popular Chettinad cuisine. Tender pieces of chicken cooked in a flavourful and freshly ground mixture of spices.

info.name: Andhra Chicken Curry
info.description: Chicken braised in yoghurt and cream, cooked in meaty stock, and seasoned to taste - all to produce a mouth watering spicy curry.

info.name: Andhra Mutton Curry
info.description: Mutton pieces braised in yoghurt and cream, cooked in meaty stock, and seasoned to taste - all to produce a mouth watering spicy curry.

info.name: Basmati Biryani Rice (400 Grams)
info.description: Long grain Basmati Biryani Rice

info.name: Malabar Paratha
info.description: Heavy layered levened bread made from flat wheat.

info.name: Double Ka Meetha
info.description: Soft milk bread soaked in a luscious saffron syrup, sprinkled with an array of dry fruits and a pinch of cardamom.

info.name: Gulab Jamun
info.description: Soft delicious berry sized balls made of milk solids, flour & a leavening agent.

info.name: Extra Raita
info.description: Fusion of yogurt with spice powders, herbs & veggies like onions, cucumbers & carrots, usually accompanied with biryani, pulao and kababs.

info.name: Extra Salan
info.description: A thin gravy,made with ingredients like peanuts, sesame seeds, coconut to form the base.
